00:02:18.144 --> 00:02:21.120
♪Vent qui passe♪

00:02:21.536 --> 00:02:24.736
♪Entrelace mes cheveux dans la danse♪

00:02:26.688 --> 00:02:31.168
♪Je me pencherai dans ses bras♪

00:02:31.776 --> 00:02:34.816
♪Traverser les mers profondes♪

00:02:35.232 --> 00:02:38.208
♪Bain d'affection♪

00:02:38.624 --> 00:02:40.704
♪Se condense en pluie♪

00:02:52.920 --> 00:02:53.888
Hé.

00:02:54.720 --> 00:02:55.760
Hé. Réveille-toi.

00:02:56.360 --> 00:02:57.440
(Est-il mort ?)

00:02:58.040 --> 00:03:00.200
(Les autorités vont-elles remonter jusqu'à moi ?)

00:03:01.080 --> 00:03:02.440
Hé.

00:03:03.000 --> 00:03:03.904
Hé.

00:03:04.120 --> 00:03:06.880
Réveillez-vous.

00:03:07.840 --> 00:03:08.840
(Dieu merci. Il est vivant.)

00:03:10.200 --> 00:03:11.136
Hé.

00:03:13.880 --> 00:03:14.960
Êtes-vous d'accord?

00:03:15.720 --> 00:03:17.000
Alors je vais partir maintenant.

00:03:26.640 --> 00:03:28.120
(Pourquoi délire-t-il ?)

00:03:28.800 --> 00:03:30.680
(Ai-je échoué à éliminer complètement
le poison de l'amour ?)

00:03:45.880 --> 00:03:46.816
Descendez!

00:04:37.000 --> 00:04:37.856
Mon seigneur.

00:04:38.040 --> 00:04:38.920
Gao Fu.

00:04:39.160 --> 00:04:40.200
Tu t'es enfin réveillé.

00:04:41.840 --> 00:04:43.720
Tu as été empoisonné,

00:04:44.400 --> 00:04:45.248
mais heureusement,

00:04:45.440 --> 00:04:46.480
il a été retiré à temps.

00:04:46.920 --> 00:04:47.840
Tu vas bien maintenant.

00:04:48.400 --> 00:04:49.520
Quand tu es arrivé hier soir,

00:04:50.960 --> 00:04:52.440
Est-ce que je me suis comporté de manière inappropriée ?

00:04:52.560 --> 00:04:53.720
(Gao Fu, Censeur)
Quand je suis arrivé,

00:04:54.280 --> 00:04:55.360
il y avait des cadavres partout.

00:04:55.960 --> 00:04:57.320
Quand je t'ai trouvé,

00:04:58.040 --> 00:05:00.600
cette dame t'appelait.

00:05:03.080 --> 00:05:05.280
Craignant qu'elle soit une assassine,
je l'ai arrêtée

00:05:05.520 --> 00:05:06.560
et j'attendais ton ordre.

00:05:07.040 --> 00:05:07.960
Alors elle et moi...

00:05:08.040 --> 00:05:09.560
Il ne s'est rien passé entre nous.

00:05:09.920 --> 00:05:13.120
Hier soir, tu m'as supplié
de te détoxifier.

00:05:13.600 --> 00:05:15.120
Puis tu es soudainement devenu fou.

00:05:15.480 --> 00:05:16.960
Pendant la lutte,

00:05:17.160 --> 00:05:18.520
tu t'es effondré inconscient.

00:05:19.440 --> 00:05:20.960
Je pensais que tu étais mort,

00:05:21.320 --> 00:05:22.640
alors j'ai continué à t'appeler.

00:05:23.360 --> 00:05:25.360
Et puis il est arrivé.

00:05:26.112 --> 00:05:27.040
Droite.

00:05:27.040 --> 00:05:28.064
Bien.

00:05:30.080 --> 00:05:31.800
Mais pourquoi l'avez-vous demandé, mon seigneur ?

00:05:32.080 --> 00:05:33.056
Aucune raison.

00:05:34.040 --> 00:05:36.080
Avez-vous identifié ces assassins ?

00:05:36.640 --> 00:05:37.760
Nous avons éliminé

00:05:38.560 --> 00:05:39.560
tous les embusqués sont dehors.

00:05:39.960 --> 00:05:41.080
Nous en avons gardé un en vie.

00:05:41.520 --> 00:05:45.480
Mais je ne m'attendais pas à ce qu'il
se suicide, sans laisser aucune information.

00:05:46.520 --> 00:05:48.960
Cependant, ils avaient tous un tatouage
sur les mains.

00:05:56.520 --> 00:05:57.440
Voici le modèle.

00:05:57.880 --> 00:05:59.960
Mais aucun document ne correspond à ce chiffre dans nos archives.

00:06:00.720 --> 00:06:05.000
Il semble que la préfecture de Ningzhou
soit vraiment extraordinaire.

00:06:05.080 --> 00:06:05.920
Peut-être,

00:06:06.720 --> 00:06:09.360
ce tatouage pourrait être notre percée.

00:06:10.560 --> 00:06:11.720
Comprenez-le tout de suite.

00:06:11.840 --> 00:06:12.768
Oui.

00:06:13.888 --> 00:06:14.848
Mon seigneur.

00:06:15.920 --> 00:06:16.800
Cette dame...

00:06:18.200 --> 00:06:19.480
- Faites-la taire.
- Oui.

00:06:20.720 --> 00:06:21.640
Attendez.

00:06:22.160 --> 00:06:23.000
Tu as un dernier mot ?

00:06:23.160 --> 00:06:24.520
J'ai déjà vu ce tatouage.

00:06:30.240 --> 00:06:31.880
Où l'as-tu vu ?

00:06:32.280 --> 00:06:33.480
J'ai été piégé.

00:06:34.480 --> 00:06:35.680
Revenir serait dangereux.

00:06:35.920 --> 00:06:36.880
Toi seul peux m'aider.

00:06:37.040 --> 00:06:40.240
Résolvez mon problème chez la famille Lu
sur Xiaowen Road demain midi.

00:06:40.440 --> 00:06:41.312
Et je vais vous le dire.

00:06:42.240 --> 00:06:43.400
Tu oses me menacer ?

00:06:44.160 --> 00:06:45.920
Pensez d’abord à votre statut.

00:06:47.200 --> 00:06:48.880
Mon statut n'a pas d'importance.

00:06:49.320 --> 00:06:50.320
Ce qui compte c'est

00:06:51.480 --> 00:06:52.360
that I know

00:06:52.640 --> 00:06:53.920
what you want to know.

00:07:01.800 --> 00:07:05.240
(As you wished, I'm here.)

00:07:07.742 --> 00:07:09.120
(Imperial decree)

00:07:15.080 --> 00:07:16.120
I'm Prefect of Ningzhou.

00:07:16.480 --> 00:07:18.160
Greetings, my lord.

00:07:18.200 --> 00:07:20.320
- Greetings, my lord.
- Greetings, my lord.

00:07:22.040 --> 00:07:23.680
Your visit here is...

00:07:24.080 --> 00:07:27.080
Has the Young Lord
from the Duke Xuan's Mansion

00:07:27.080 --> 00:07:28.400
already arrived in Ningzhou?

00:07:28.640 --> 00:07:29.640
Gao Fu.

00:07:30.480 --> 00:07:31.440
Open it.

00:07:36.360 --> 00:07:37.376
Watch out.

00:07:46.240 --> 00:07:47.360
Lord Xia.

00:07:49.640 --> 00:07:52.320
The Young Lord was returning
to Bianzhou to visit family

00:07:52.760 --> 00:07:54.800
and stopped to rest
in Ningzhou Prefecture.

00:07:55.040 --> 00:07:56.880
Before he'd even left the capital,

00:07:57.560 --> 00:07:59.840
assassins were already lying in wait.

00:08:00.880 --> 00:08:02.840
Had I not led the vanguard,

00:08:03.480 --> 00:08:06.720
this blade would have been plunged
into his body.

00:08:09.640 --> 00:08:10.720
Tell me,

00:08:11.240 --> 00:08:12.800
who exactly is it

00:08:13.080 --> 00:08:15.160
that wants the Young Lord dead
so desperately?

00:08:15.360 --> 00:08:17.160
I will order
an investigation immediately.

00:08:17.440 --> 00:08:18.320
I'll find out swiftly

00:08:18.440 --> 00:08:19.600
and give you a full account.

00:08:20.440 --> 00:08:21.640
Lord Xia.

00:08:22.520 --> 00:08:23.760
I've searched all over Ningzhou

00:08:24.400 --> 00:08:26.120
looking for you.

00:08:27.360 --> 00:08:28.480
I'm exhausted now.

00:08:28.480 --> 00:08:29.720
Conduct the investigation here.

00:08:30.400 --> 00:08:31.360
I'll be waiting.

00:08:31.760 --> 00:08:32.600
Oui.

00:08:53.720 --> 00:08:54.800
You seem

00:08:55.640 --> 00:08:57.160
somewhat familiar to me.

00:08:58.440 --> 00:08:59.320
Lord Shen,

00:08:59.600 --> 00:09:00.600
she is my concubine.

00:09:00.600 --> 00:09:01.800
She rarely ventures out.

00:09:02.360 --> 00:09:03.480
You must be mistaken.

00:09:04.880 --> 00:09:06.080
What crime

00:09:06.240 --> 00:09:07.680
has she committed?

00:09:08.080 --> 00:09:08.960
My lord,

00:09:09.560 --> 00:09:12.200
this vile woman committed adultery
at the Goddess Temple last night,

00:09:12.800 --> 00:09:13.960
defiling the gods

00:09:14.000 --> 00:09:15.640
and causing me to lose my child.

00:09:15.840 --> 00:09:16.960
She deserves death!

00:09:17.680 --> 00:09:18.520
Lan,

00:09:18.720 --> 00:09:21.000
I don't regret loving you sincerely.

00:09:21.360 --> 00:09:23.760
We were just bound by longing,

00:09:24.320 --> 00:09:25.400
but not by fate.

00:09:29.240 --> 00:09:30.840
Then I wasn't mistaken.

00:09:31.160 --> 00:09:34.040
When I was attacked
in the temple yesterday,

00:09:36.280 --> 00:09:37.200
you were also there.

00:09:43.320 --> 00:09:45.480
Yesterday, when assassins came for me

00:09:46.200 --> 00:09:48.240
and chased me into the temple,

00:09:49.120 --> 00:09:51.440
I saw her lighting lamps alone.

00:09:51.960 --> 00:09:54.400
She got caught in the battle
because of me.

00:09:54.720 --> 00:09:56.760
If I recall correctly,

00:09:57.120 --> 00:09:58.600
all the assassins

00:09:58.800 --> 00:10:00.560
should have been slain by me.

00:10:01.960 --> 00:10:02.960
So I'd like to ask

00:10:03.600 --> 00:10:08.040
how he got away unscathed?

00:10:08.560 --> 00:10:09.408
Well...

00:10:10.720 --> 00:10:11.720
My lord,

00:10:11.720 --> 00:10:12.600
could it be

00:10:13.240 --> 00:10:14.880
he's in league with the assassins?

00:10:16.200 --> 00:10:17.240
Perfect.

00:10:17.600 --> 00:10:19.640
We've got one empty cage left.

00:10:19.800 --> 00:10:20.736
Exactly.

00:10:21.360 --> 00:10:22.200
Lord Xia.

00:10:22.800 --> 00:10:24.000
How about

00:10:24.240 --> 00:10:27.360
I sever this escaped assassin's head

00:10:27.520 --> 00:10:29.240
and deliver it to you?

00:10:29.480 --> 00:10:30.480
How's that?

00:10:30.480 --> 00:10:31.424
No.

00:10:32.160 --> 00:10:33.000
My lord!

00:10:33.080 --> 00:10:35.040
- I'm innocent, my lord!
- Shut up!

00:10:35.480 --> 00:10:36.880
Guards! Take him away.

00:10:36.880 --> 00:10:38.360
Lady Jinzhi, you promised me...

00:10:46.680 --> 00:10:47.584
My lord.

00:10:48.600 --> 00:10:49.600
Xia Jinzhi believes

00:10:50.240 --> 00:10:53.840
my failure to light her blessing lamp
in the temple

00:10:54.280 --> 00:10:56.840
caused her child to die.

00:10:57.240 --> 00:10:58.440
But I think

00:10:58.920 --> 00:11:00.280
her child's death

00:11:00.600 --> 00:11:03.040
has no connection
to whether I lit lamps or not.

00:11:04.240 --> 00:11:05.080
My lord,

00:11:05.080 --> 00:11:06.760
you know perfectly well

00:11:07.040 --> 00:11:09.080
whether I committed adultery
last night, right?

00:11:09.160 --> 00:11:10.400
Shut up!

00:11:10.920 --> 00:11:12.720
You killed my son!

00:11:14.200 --> 00:11:16.120
Whether you committed adultery

00:11:16.920 --> 00:11:18.640
is certainly clear to me.

00:11:19.600 --> 00:11:20.480
However,

00:11:20.880 --> 00:11:22.200
the notion that lamp-lighting

00:11:22.480 --> 00:11:24.520
harmed a fetus is pure nonsense.

00:11:26.000 --> 00:11:27.240
In my judgment,

00:11:27.640 --> 00:11:31.840
the deceased should be autopsied,
and the living one has check-up.

00:11:32.840 --> 00:11:35.240
We'll get to the bottom of it today.

